      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANGAR COUNTY (7) is an A Barnes-trained newcomer by Bernardo out of Nangar Silk. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Market moves likely to signal ability but profiles strongly for this. POKE THE GLASS (1) will take beating coming off a good 18.82 win at Temora over 330m. Top win latest and rates a key player again. ROXY KEEPING (5) turned in a moderate performance last time when sixth at this track over 318m behind Clarice Keeping (19.06) in a Maiden. Was in the money prior to that. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Shapes as one to consider. TOTAL TEMPTATION (2) is a newcomer from the Leighton Winter kennel. Gets every chance from the inside draw. Can run a bold race on debut.",
